spans.text: my lone passage through this vale of life
my labouring breast With high sensations : awful silence reigns Above , around ; the sounding winds no more Wild through the fluctuating forest fly With gust impetuous
in sequestered woods , And deep-embowering shades
the fleet shadows over the waving plains
the fleet shadows over the waving plains
of their dance In rings mysterious to the passing swain
no more A safe retirement to the hostile bands
Wheels the night raven shrill , with hideous note Portending death to the dejected swain
Portending death to the dejected swain
his beams Impartial , cheering other skies and shores
Where ( thought stupendous ! ) systems infinite , In regular confusion
Who search for bliss in the capacious bowl , And blindly woo Intemperance for Joy
that frighted fly The dark intrigue , and midnight masquerade ; What is this pleasure which inchants mankind ?
The etherial spark divine to brute transformed
the Nymph he styles A foe to pleasure
